title: Only 1 Left!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Trinity Park Apartments', 'Spacious 1 bedroom floorplan comes with wood-style plank flooring*, black cabinets, black appliances*, and two-tone paint.', 'Full size washer/dryer hook-ups are in every home and the closet space is something dreams are made of.', 'A refreshing pool (open seasonally) and picnic areas are available for your enjoyment, and there is plenty of parking throughout the community.', 'Make your appointment today and come see your new home!', '(*In select units)', 'Professionally Managed by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc., TX - License # 9003183', '-Carpeting', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Spacious Closets', '-Breakfast Nook', '-Den', '-Full Size Washer and Dryer Hookups', '-Air Conditioner', '-Refrigerator', '-Ceiling Fan', '-Night Patrol', '-Efficient Appliances', '-Plank Flooring', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
